    • addAnalogPressureSensor

      public void addAnalogPressureSensor​(int analog_channel)
      Creates an analog pressure sensor based on the REV Analog Pressure Sensor.

      Only need to do this if using PCM. Otherwise just plug the sensor into analog port 0 on the PH.

    • addAnalogPressureSensor

      public void addAnalogPressureSensor​(int analog_channel, double fullRange, double offset)
      Creates an analog pressure sensor with given full range and offset.

      Only need to do this if using PCM. Otherwise just plug the sensor into analog port 0 on the PH.

      Parameters:
      analog_channel - Analog port the sensor is plugged into.
      fullRange - Scaling multiplier to output (check with part manufacturer).
      offset - Offset added to scaled value.

    • getPressure

    • enableAnalog

      public void enableAnalog​(double minPressure, double maxPressure)
      Enables closed loop compressor control using analog input from REV Analog Pressure Sensor only. Defaults to digital control if CTRE PCM.
      Parameters:
      minPressure - Compressor enables when pressure is below this value.
      maxPressure - Compressor disables when pressure is above this value.

    • enableHybrid

      public void enableHybrid​(double minPressure, double maxPressure)
      Enables closed loop compressor control using hybrid input from REV Analog Pressure Sensor only. Defaults to digital control if CTRE PCM.
      Parameters:
      minPressure - Compressor enables when pressure is below this value.
      maxPressure - Compressor disables when pressure is above this value.
